  mkdir -p .cursor/rules

  cat > .cursor/rules/forgeteam.mdc <<'EOF'
---
description: ForgeTeam AI Development Framework
globs: ["**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

# ForgeTeam Rules for Cursor

## Session Start
Load context from .forgeteam/memory/ and .forgeteam/config.yaml

## Workflow
1. Auto-detect route: micro (<50 lines) / standard / full (>500 lines)
2. Follow skill-specific instructions
3. Verify before shipping: Build → Test → Run → Safety
4. Update .forgeteam/memory/state.md after actions
5. Keep documentation in sync with code changes

## Key Files
- .forgeteam/config.yaml — Project configuration
- .forgeteam/memory/state.md — Current state
